*ppp-2.4.1-r12 (15 Dec 2002)

  15 Dec 2002; phoen][x <phoenix@gentoo.org> ppp-2.4.1-r12.ebuild, ChangeLog,
  files/digest-ppp-2.4.1-r12 :
